{"tid":1630320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫生朋友同我講左個好正既比喻 笑你班港島撚","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:33:54.000Z","uid":197608,"like":111,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2498b124574def70ed31c1975d0d98e40a58a08c","tid":1630320,"uid":197608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:06:09.000Z","msg":"癌症集中係一個位置都仲有希望 就有得醫<br />\n當擴散左之後病人就要打定輸數"},{"pid":"da2b51bb0620df42188c445d80014d1fb80dea69","tid":1630320,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:07:24.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"1eb5cdc4a861e1e260680b0e86f8488dce6b87cf","tid":1630320,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:08:42.000Z","msg":"邊個大大聲話集中<br />\n<br />\n鞭屍時間<br />\n<br />\n集中撚答到我問題，先好叫人出黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9c3250bc69b9a2b72eabec9fa37a133289a1a615","tid":1630320,"uid":197608,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:21.000Z","msg":"更何況講緊既係30000個邪惡白血球 對上200萬善良既癌細胞"},{"pid":"6da85da1b3bfa8d6c59d867078d8b894030b7700","tid":1630320,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"話你知咩叫和勇合一<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630017</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9d5bbc5e2e4c77c0698d19f0bf5696ac5621474c","tid":1630320,"uid":41608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46804699506b682fa345aac680d5dbd8ecf9efb0","tid":1630320,"uid":197608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"01d23d43e9e7772dc4cb3d95ffb6a8f687940e8a","tid":1630320,"uid":253016,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:33.000Z","msg":"大遊行既作用係宣言 表達市民既意願<br />\n<br />\n流水先係真正既示威"},{"pid":"752bc1468396bb8f1f2e46243244f67f5909874e","tid":1630320,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"4909796843b598420e07bf6f316f30407ebf01d5","tid":1630320,"uid":51840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:14:46.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"0fee5ebf2052a88938a9850e80487c7801182c52","tid":1630320,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b3a76579de75a7ebf69b6cc102511634aebbf81","tid":1630320,"uid":259675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:15:10.000Z","msg":"呢個比喻唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13c0d7a0c59ab942e8a975795a494f8f8195039","tid":1630320,"u